These are Puzzles for 7x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 7x4-Level-4-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, iced-tea, soy-milk, sprite
There 4 different types of food: blueberry, eggplant, lemon, nectarine
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, snowmobile, bongani-climbing, ship
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, december, january, august
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, oliveros, vegafina, bongani
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, lizard, mouse, rabbit
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: zinnia, tulip, dahlia, marigold
 1. the tiparillo-smoker is on the far right##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in december is the person eating eggplant##1
 3. the person eating nectarine is the owner of the lizard##1
 4. the owner of the mouse is the person eating eggplant##1
 5. the person who growsdahlia is between the person who growszinnia and the person driving the bongani-climbing##2
 6. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
 7. the person drinking 7up is the owner of the goldfish##1
 8. the person drinking 7up is in an odd position##4
 9. the person who's birthday is in january is the person drinking iced-tea##1
10. the person drinking soy-milk is in an even position##4
11. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person who growsdahlia##3
12. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the person who growstulip##3
13. the person eating lemon is on the left of the bongani-smoker##1
14. the person eating nectarine is on the far left or far right##3
15. the person who's birthday is in april is on the far left##1
16. the person drinking sprite is in an odd position##4
17. the owner of the rabbit is on the far left or far right##3
18. the owner of the rabbit is the person who growsmarigold##1
19. the oliveros-smoker is the person eating blueberry##1
20. the vegafina-smoker is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
21. the person who's birthday is in december is the person eating eggplant##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage      | sprite        | soy-milk   | 7up         | iced-tea  |
| Food          | lemon         | eggplant   | blueberry   | nectarine |
| Transport         | bongani-climbing | snowmobile    | ship | quad-bike   |
| Birthday   | april        | december  | august      | january   |
| Cigar   | vegafina          | bongani       | oliveros        | tiparillo   |
| Pet           | rabbit        | mouse      | goldfish    | lizard    |
| Flower         | marigold | dahlia | zinnia      | tulip   |

