The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, scientist, designer, nurse
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, indie, metal, trance
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, july, april, august
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: mystery, western, drama, crime
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, ice-hockey, skateboarding, volleyball
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, filmmaking, singing, board-games
 1. the scientist is on the left or right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##3
 2. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left or right of the fan of metal##3
 3. the person who's birthday is in march is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the bartender is on the left or right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##3
 5. the bartender is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 6. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the fan of indie##1
 7. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is singing##3
 8. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3
 9. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left or right of the fan of folk##3
10. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the far right##1
11. the person who's hobby is gardening is the person who's birthday is in april##1
12. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
13. the person watching mystery movies is on the left or right of the bartender##3
14. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
15. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left or right of the designer##3
16. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the nurse##1
17. the person who's birthday is in august is in an even position##4
18. the person watching western movies is the person who's hobby is board-games##1
19. the fan of trance is on the far left or far right##3
20. the fan of folk is in an odd position##4
21. the nurse is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |     3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | fanta         | coffee     | tea        | mirinda  |
| Job          | designer          | bartender     | nurse    | scientist   |
| Music-Genre   | folk          | metal      | indie      | trance   |
