 7. the person playing go is the person who growsorchid##1
 8. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the far right##1
 9. the person playing go is in an odd position##4
10. the person watching zombie movies is on the left or right of the person who growsbellflower##3
11. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left or right of the person eating apple##3
12. the person eating lemon is the person playing scrabble##1
13. the person playing poker is in an even position##4
14. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person who growsbellflower##1
15. the cottage house is on the left or right of the person watching scientific movies##3
16. the cottage house is on the left of the futuristic house##1
17. the person watching horror movies is the person who's sport is basketball##1
18. the modern house is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
19. the person watching family movies is on the left or right of the person who growsorchid##3

.:: Answer ::.
