.:: Puzzle 7x4-Level-4-4::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, bike, ship, boat
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, hiking, rock-climbing, traveling
House: colonial, cape-cod, tower, palace
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, folk, soul, techno
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, dutch, nigerian, spanish
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, montecristo, chaman, vegafina
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, october, february, march
 1. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in march##3
 2. the fan of folk is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##3
 3. the tower house is on the right of the chaman-smoker##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in november is in an even position##4
 5. the person who's birthday is in february is in an odd position##4
 6. the spanish is on the left or right of the montecristo-smoker##3
 7. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the dutch##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left or right of the fan of techno##3
 9. the palace house is in an odd position##4
10. the person driving the ship is on the right of the montecristo-smoker##1
11. the fan of d&b is on the right of the dutch##1
12. the montecristo-smoker is on the left or right of the canadian##3
13. the person who's hobby is board-games is in an odd position##4
14. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
15. the canadian is between the person who's hobby is hiking and the person who's birthday is in february##2
16. the fan of folk is between the colonial house and the chaman-smoker##2
17. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the far left or far right##3
18. the person driving the boat is on the left of the old-henry-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |      3      |     4      |
| Transport          | bike | motorbike        | boat  | ship     |
| Hobby         | hiking    | rock-climbing | board-games | traveling  |
| House   | palace | cape-cod  | tower     | colonial   |
| Music-Genre   | techno    | d&b           | folk        | soul       |
| Nationality   | dutch     | canadian      | nigerian    | spanish    |
| Cigar           | vegafina    | chaman         | montecristo    | old-henry |
