 7. the person watching sports movies is the person eating peas##1
 8. the cape-cod house is on the left or right of the person who growsiris##3
 9. the person who likes red is on the left or right of the person who likes purple##3
10. the person who likes coral is on the left of the person who growsiris##1
11. the person driving the train is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
12. the person watching epic movies is on the left or right of the person watching romance movies##3
